  "description": "This test case evaluates the ability to identify patients with appendicitis using the PheKB eMERGE algorithm. The phenotype identifies cases through: (1) pathology-confirmed appendicitis, (2) treatment with systemic antibiotics >2 days, or (3) interventional radiology procedures. The algorithm excludes patients with comorbidities that mimic appendicitis symptoms and incidental appendectomies.",
